Package json

Class JSONNumber

java.lang.Object
json.JSONValue
json.JSONNumber
public class JSONNumber extends JSONValue
Represents an immutable JSON number value.

The actual type of the stored value is determined by which version of the constructor is called.

Rather than store everything as double, the appropriate type is used, to save space and to also ensure the value is displayed correctly when output as a string, i.e. integer type values do not include the fractional part.
Author:
mdixon
